  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Education in rural South Africa - Vehicle needed</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Children in the valley have broad smiles, frantic waving and greetings when they see our vehicle. They know that YOUPSA is bringing unforgettable creative learning with fun to them. BUT these schools are difficult to access and our current vehicle cannot travel these rough paths and farm roads. YOUPSA needs to get a strong 2nd-hand SUV for bringing educational and art programs to rural disadvantaged children and schools. Without this we are stuck.</narrative>
  </description>
